OL,5, Care sector bosses in England are      
OL,6, struggling to recruit staff, with more 
OL,7, jobs unfilled than before the pandemic,
OL,8, says a leading industry body.          
OL,10,FThe number of unfilled jobs fell at the
OL,11,Fstart of the pandemic but rose this    
OL,12,Fyear as the economy opened up, suggests
OL,13,Fanalysis by Skills for Care.           
OL,15,FEmployers are also finding it harder to
OL,16,Fkeep existing staff, the report finds. 
OL,18,FThe government says extra funding and a
OL,19,Fregular recruitment drive will help    
OL,20,Fboost the workforce.                   
